00:42:11,893 --> 00:42:14,145
- Ada masalah?
- Ketua?

456
00:42:15,354 --> 00:42:16,397
<i>Setelah hari itu,</i>

457
00:42:16,481 --> 00:42:19,525
<i>rumor dia kehilangan kejantanan</i>

458
00:42:19,609 --> 00:42:21,611
<i>tersebar seperti legenda.</i>

459
00:42:22,111 --> 00:42:26,616
<i>Itu juga saat dia mulai mengomeliku
tanpa sebab yang jelas.</i>

460
00:42:28,201 --> 00:42:29,827
<i>Kita hanya punya satu menit.</i>

461
00:42:30,286 --> 00:42:33,623
<i>Jika bertahan semenit lagi,
